For some reason, it won't let me post the Pastebin link. Sorry about that. You can google up for the direct Vimeo links they use on Project Go. 

1. Get Firefox
2. Install Tamper Data
3. Open Tamper Data
4. Copy the Vimeo link you'd like to watch
5. Click "Start Tamper"
6. Paste the Vimeo link in the bar and hit enter.
7. It will ask you if you want to edit, you hit edit/yes. (I don't remember the exact phrasing)
8. Change the Referer field to "http://www.simplepickup.com"
9. Enjoy.

1. Go the SimplePickup forum and sign in.
2. Go to any open topic.
3. Go under the quick response and click "Go Advanced"
4. Paste the link to the body as if your going to reply to the topic.
5. Click "Preview Post". http://i.imgur.com/pfy0c.png
6. Press link now and you should have access to the video on Vimeo. http://i.imgur.com/ocM0O.png
